                                        <div class="reply-line" style="margin-right: 10px; height: 15px;"></div>
                                        <div class="reply-not-loaded-svg">
                                            <svg class="replyIcon_c19a55" width="12" height="8" viewBox="0 0 12 8">
                                                <path d="M0.809739 3.59646L5.12565 0.468433C5.17446 0.431163 5.23323 0.408043 5.2951 0.401763C5.35698 0.395482 5.41943 0.406298 5.4752 0.432954C5.53096 0.45961 5.57776 0.50101 5.61013 0.552343C5.64251 0.603676 5.65914 0.662833 5.6581 0.722939V2.3707C10.3624 2.3707 11.2539 5.52482 11.3991 7.21174C11.4028 7.27916 11.3848 7.34603 11.3474 7.40312C11.3101 7.46021 11.2554 7.50471 11.1908 7.53049C11.1262 7.55626 11.0549 7.56204 10.9868 7.54703C10.9187 7.53201 10.857 7.49695 10.8104 7.44666C8.72224 5.08977 5.6581 5.63359 5.6581 5.63359V7.28135C5.65831 7.34051 5.64141 7.39856 5.60931 7.44894C5.5772 7.49932 5.53117 7.54004 5.4764 7.5665C5.42163 7.59296 5.3603 7.60411 5.29932 7.59869C5.23834 7.59328 5.18014 7.57151 5.13128 7.53585L0.809739 4.40892C0.744492 4.3616 0.691538 4.30026 0.655067 4.22975C0.618596 4.15925 0.599609 4.08151 0.599609 4.00269C0.599609 3.92386 0.618596 3.84612 0.655067 3.77562C0.691538 3.70511 0.744492 3.64377 0.809739 3.59646Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                                            </svg>
                                        </div>
                                        <br/>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="reply-text-container">
                                        <div class="reply-text">Не удается загрузить сообщение</div>
                                    </div>
                                </a>

                            </div>

                            <div class="message-header">
                                <span class="username"></span>
